Uses of such Technologies fall into the following general categories:

Operationally Necessary. Cookies, web beacons, or other similar technologies that are necessary to the operation of the Business Services, Properties, websites, applications, and tools. This includes Technologies that are required to identify irregular site behavior, prevent fraudulent activity and improve security or that allow you to make use of our functions such as shopping-carts, saved search, or similar functions;
Performance Related. Cookies, web beacons, or other similar technologies are used to assess the performance of Business Services, Properties, websites, applications, and tools, including as part of standard analytic and measurement practices to help understand how visitors use the Business Services, Properties, websites, and applications and interact with messaging, or view an item or link;
Functionality Related. Cookies, web beacons, or other similar Technologies that offer enhanced functionality. This may include identifying you when you sign into a Property, website, application or Business Service or keeping track of your specified preferences, interests, or past items viewed so that we, our Clients and third parties may enhance the Business Services, Properties, websites, applications, and tools;
Advertising or Targeting Related. First-party and third-party cookies and web beacons deliver content, including ads relevant to your interests, through our Business Services, Properties or on third party websites and applications. This includes using Technologies to understand the usefulness to you of the advertisements and content that has been delivered to you, such as whether you have clicked on an advertisement.

